
  Treecko    Grass Type Pokémon

  TREECKO has small hooks on the 
  bottom of its feet that enable 
  it to scale vertical walls.  
  Treecko attacks by slamming 
  foes with its thick tail. 
	   Evolution Chain
  Treecko ► Grovyle ► Sceptile

